## 🔹 **6. Servlet Programs**

- ➗ Calculate factorial using Servlet & HTML form
- 🍪 Create a cookie for name and show visit count
- 🔢 Check if a number is prime using Servlet

---

## 🔹 **7. JSP – Session & Cookie Management**

- 🕒 Session-based greeting with 1-minute timeout
- 🍪 Add cookie with name, domain, expiry and display all cookies

---

## 🔹 **8. JSP + JDBC – Coffee & Employee Management**

- ☕ Insert a new coffee product (id, name, price)
- 🔁 Update a coffee product by ID
- 👨‍💼 Insert employee (empno, name, salary) and generate a **Salary Report**
- ✏️ Update employee details using form input

---

## 🔹 **9. JSP + JDBC – Queries and Deletions**

- ❌ Delete a coffee product by ID and show remaining
- 🔍 Display all coffee names starting with **D**
- ➕ Insert employees and generate salary report
- ❌ Delete employees whose name starts with **S**

---

✅ **Note**: All programs include user input, backend logic using Java, and output displayed via console, GUI, or browser using JSP/Servlet.

